Talk given at WPCF (Workshop on Particle Correlations and Femtoscopy)
  2008, Krakow, Poland. Proceedings to be published in Acta Physica Polonica B;
  18 pages, 10 figures;

14 pages, 14 figures, submitted to the MNRAS. See animations at
